+ * when @event is the obj that signaled the wait.  One-shot — first
+ * consumer wins; the staged entry is cleared atomically under obj_lock.
+ * No-op if no pending boost.
+ *
+ * Closes a fast-path race in the previous "find target at SET_PI time"
+ * design: a waiter that took obj_lock first, saw signaled=true and
+ * returned without queueing was never visible to event->any_waiters,
+ * so no target could be captured and no boost was applied — observed
